Leterme Pledges to Protect Dexia Bank Belgium Account Holders

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-04T20:11:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/leterme-pledges-to-protect-dexia-bank-belgium-account-holders.html
Belgian Prime Minister  Yves Leterme 
said the government would protect account holders at Dexia Bank
Belgium.  “The government will make sure that no client of Dexia
Bank Belgium will lose a single euro cent,” Leterme told a
press conference today in Brussels.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  